<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Data Cleaning & Visualization</title>

<style>
*{
margin:0;
padding:0;
box-sizing:border-box;
font-family:Arial, sans-serif;
}

body{
background:#f4f7fc;
}

header{
background:#2563eb;
color:white;
padding:20px;
text-align:center;
font-size:28px;
font-weight:bold;
}

.container{
width:90%;
max-width:1100px;
margin:30px auto;
}

.card{
background:white;
padding:25px;
border-radius:12px;
box-shadow:0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
margin-bottom:30px;
}

h2{
color:#2563eb;
margin-bottom:15px;
}

p{
color:#555;
line-height:1.7;
}

.upload-box{
border:2px dashed #2563eb;
padding:40px;
text-align:center;
border-radius:10px;
margin-top:20px;
}

input[type=file]{
margin:20px;
}

button{
background:#2563eb;
color:white;
border:none;
padding:12px 25px;
font-size:16px;
border-radius:6px;
cursor:pointer;
}

button:hover{
background:#1d4ed8;
}

.features{
display:grid;
grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(220px,1fr));
gap:20px;
margin-top:20px;
}

.feature{
background:#eef4ff;
padding:20px;
border-radius:10px;
text-align:center;
}

.feature h3{
margin-bottom:10px;
color:#2563eb;
}

.dashboard{
display:grid;
grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(250px,1fr));
gap:20px;
margin-top:20px;
}

.chart{
background:white;
height:220px;
border-radius:10px;
display:flex;
justify-content:center;
align-items:center;
border:2px dashed #bbb;
font-size:20px;
color:#888;
}

footer{
text-align:center;
padding:20px;
background:#2563eb;
color:white;
margin-top:30px;
}
</style>

</head>

<body>

<header>
Data Cleaning & Visualization Dashboard
</header>

<div class="container">

<div class="card">
<h2>Project Overview</h2>
<p>
Upload a CSV dataset, clean missing values, remove duplicates,
detect outliers, and visualize the cleaned data.
</p>

<div class="upload-box">
<h3>Upload Dataset</h3>

<input type="file">

<br>

<button>Upload Dataset</button>

</div>
</div>

<div class="card">

<h2>Data Cleaning Features</h2>

<div class="features">

<div class="feature">
<h3>Missing Values</h3>
<p>Automatically detects and fills missing values.</p>
</div>

<div class="feature">
<h3>Duplicates</h3>
<p>Removes duplicate records from dataset.</p>
</div>

<div class="feature">
<h3>Outliers</h3>
<p>Detects abnormal values using statistical methods.</p>
</div>

<div class="feature">
<h3>Download</h3>
<p>Download the cleaned dataset instantly.</p>
</div>

</div>

</div>

<div class="card">

<h2>Data Visualization</h2>

<div class="dashboard">

<div class="chart">
Bar Chart
</div>

<div class="chart">
Pie Chart
</div>

<div class="chart">
Histogram
</div>

<div class="chart">
Line Chart
</div>

<div class="chart">
Scatter Plot
</div>

<div class="chart">
Box Plot
</div>

</div>

</div>

</div>

<footer>

© 2026 Data Cleaning & Visualization Project

</footer>

</body>
</html>